requests.description:
The array of update requests. Check out the Google Docs API Documentation [here](https://developers.google.com/docs/api/reference/rest/v1/documents/request).

SAMPLE INPUT:
```
const insertNewParagraphRequest = {
    insertText: {
        location: {
            index: 1, // Index where you want to insert a new paragraph
        },
        text: "\n", // Inserting a newline to create a new paragraph
    }
};

const insertTextRequest = {
    insertText: {
        location: {
            index: 2, // Index within the new paragraph to insert text
        },
        text: "Inserted text here",
    }
};

const requests = [insertNewParagraphRequest, insertTextRequest];
return requests;
```

